      <li>Open-source platforms, frameworks and components</li>
      <li>Test automation</li>
      <li>Continuous integration and deployment</li>
    </ul>

  <h2>Coaching</h2>
  <p>Besides the software work I've also done quite a bit of personal <em>coaching</em>, mostly related to
