<p>Coaching is about personal development and change. It's about clarifying your thoughts and direction in a methodic way.
It's about developing the mental skill and flexibility to solve any problem that the life throws at you.
</p>
<p>
<blockquote>If you want to get on overview of my way of thinking, check out my book
